tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"鬼佬辦學俾所有人讀，你班華人就攪世襲壟斷，正一垃圾民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a903cf9a18d0a12d75d4777bf14eddb3cf94506","tid":834420,"uid":198245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:47:59.000Z","msg":"你想讀名校就係為咗名校啲資源/網絡。如果唔咁樣收生同普通學校一樣仲有鬼人報咩。"},{"pid":"06067dd519f801bbba7dca02863d0ceacf4a43aa","tid":834420,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"港英時代真係比較多公屋子弟讀到名校<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在就係玩5毛戰,吹撚到名校只收有錢人係好有道理"},{"pid":"b9c70d3445f37c01d0f9263c626dc937d0e8c78d","tid":834420,"uid":45636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:05:55.000Z","msg":"唔比蝗入 做得唔錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff326e2fbacc40d4687d9628cc75b5220149af6","tid":834420,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26e01d7fffbc59ebaa6f623118f4b3ccc5b398e0","tid":834420,"uid":1740,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:08:27.000Z","msg":"喇沙咪係咁<br />\n連登好多分人等的垃圾"},{"pid":"4ff82c81654ce42c79b52687c6bd02e5d26d8956","tid":834420,"uid":42949,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:12:25.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<br />\n父母有錢自然培育到能力好既學生"},{"pid":"bb16c8ee5a19abcdd3d3eda4133db48a061137b7","tid":834420,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"罷課吖笨"},{"pid":"fa969244c238fcf72e20ba31f5c8445f38a8a1c9","tid":834420,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:20:12.000Z","msg":"外國教會學校都係咁，有乜咁奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0152f2356f5d049078524874e12dc4f9c2cbe54b","tid":834420,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccbc7e4dfb2437ec01b0d156dad8f624ac3c8c14","tid":834420,"uid":22701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:57:24.000Z","msg":"趕絕的蝗入去讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T23:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}